title: Kadena's
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Laid-back quiet atmosphere with a view and koi pond. Veg choices such as vegetables sauteed with linguini pasta in a hot bean-peanut sauce, spicy Thai coconut-curry sauce, rotini pasta, and vegetables sauteed in a tomato, rosemary and roasted garlic sauce, along with salads. Vegans ask for no cheese on the eggplant sandwich.
